name: Upcoming Events Query Report
query:
SELECT
    event_name AS "Event Name:Data",
    start_date AS "Start Date:Date",
    end_date AS "End Date:Date",
    capacity AS "Capacity:Int",
    registered AS "Registered:Int"
FROM
    `tabEvent Doctype`
WHERE
    start_date >= CURDATE()
ORDER BY
    start_date ASC;
